Install python spidev
https://www.raspberrypi.org/forums/viewtopic.php?t=56669

Install other required packages available thru pip
sudo python -m pip install -r requirements.txt

The latest version of wxpython available thru pip is 3.0.something, we need 4.0.0b2.
Install following these directions, but don't bother with the python 3.x crap, just use 2.7
https://wiki.wxpython.org/BuildWxPythonOnRaspberryPi